                        description "0x8864/PPPoE Session/Broadcast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                            etype 0x8864
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 866 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8864/PPPoE Session/Multicast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac 01:00:5e:00:00:00 ff:ff:ff:80:00:00
                            etype 0x8864
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 899 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8864/PPPoE Session/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            etype 0x8864
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 933 create
                        action accept
                        description "Others/Others/Broadcast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 966 create
                        action accept
                        description "Others/Others/Multicast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac 01:00:5e:00:00:00 ff:ff:ff:80:00:00
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 999 create
                        action accept
                        description "Others/Others/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                        exit
                    exit
                    no shutdown
                exit
            exit
        exit
    exit

echo "Filter Configuration"
#--------------------------------------------------
    filter 
        ip-filter 10 create
            default-action forward
            description "limit_www" 
            entry 10 create
                match protocol tcp
                    src-port eq 80
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 20 create
                match protocol tcp
                    src-port eq 8080
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 30 create
                match protocol udp
                    src-port eq 80
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 40 create
                match protocol udp
                    src-port eq 8080
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
        exit 
        ip-filter 20 create
            default-action forward
            description "limit_www" 
            entry 10 create
                match protocol tcp
                    dst-port eq 80
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 20 create
                match protocol tcp
                    dst-port eq 8080
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 30 create
                match protocol udp
                    dst-port eq 80
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 40 create
                match protocol udp
                    dst-port eq 8080
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
        exit 
        ip-filter 40 create
            default-action forward
            entry 10 create
                match protocol tcp
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
        exit 
        ip-filter 100 create
            default-action forward
            entry 10 create
                log 101
                action
                    forward
                exit
            exit 
        exit 
        ip-filter 445 create
            default-action forward
            entry 10 create
                match protocol tcp
                    dst-port eq 445
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 20 create
                match protocol udp
                    dst-port eq 445
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
        exit 
    exit
